==Russian==
[[Category:Russian numbers]]
===Etymology===
Borrowed from Greek '''[[τεσσαράκοντα]]''' (40) as a result of Russian trade in [[Byzantium]].

===Cardinal number===
'''сорок''' (sórok)

#[[forty]] (40)
#:*Last: [[тридцать девять]] (39)
#:*Next: [[сорок один]] (41), [[пятьдесят]] (50)

:''Usage note: '''''сорок''''' in the [[nominative case]] governs the [[genitive]] [[plural]] of the noun.''
:*сорок [[книга|книг]] — ''forty books''
:*[[книга|книг]] сорок — ''approximately forty books''

